               type="paratext"><rs ref="#pmb11988" type="person"
                  >Kraus</rs> – diverses<lb xml:id="uuid_a27b77ef-e271-4445-977d-9da1d73a2a0d"/>28.
               MRZ. 1935</note>
         </p>
